himg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":664975526,"title":"《黑神话：悟空》2017年开始开发，如何知道2024年的显卡性能？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/664975526","type":"question","created":1724290961,"answer_count":27,"follower_count":92,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1045,4401,601256],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我理解一开始的工作并不会对硬件性能提出要求，那么是到哪个工作步骤，开始对硬件性能提出要求的？（或者说，需要开始考虑硬件能力和质量的平衡）"},"attached_info":"Cj8IhtTp3faKoNEcEAMaCTExMDA0OTgxOCCRr5q2BjAAOFxABXIJNjY0OTc1NTI2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"192 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8441d39e77aced623e82be6404fcd9cc_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1724739782.218182","card_id":"Q_664891274","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":664891274,"title":"收到了西北工业大学课题组的回信，我是否应该放弃科研，专注工程开发？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/664891274","type":"question","created":1724226876,"answer_count":86,"follower_count":234,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2232,7561,36894,89794],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"所以我现在的诉求是探讨科研和工程，考研和读研的区别也很大，如果以后自己有读研的打算，我也想了解一下科研是什么，如果我不适合做研究，我就立刻止损，不在自己不擅长的领域死磕。 ——（分界线） 去年考研咨询了西工大课题组，但给我归类都是“工程开发”，并不是“科研”。 回信内容如下： 我感觉就是做工程和科研，没有高低贵贱之分吧（都是为了提升生产力），自己做工程开发的话，也会考虑到设计模式、高内聚低耦合这些的，感觉也会动脑子吧。 现在感觉的是，企业的工程开发好像更接近生产力一点（个人感觉）。 我的邮件在这个回答里面：收到了西北工业大学课题组的回信，我是否应该放弃科研，专注工程开发？ ——（补充） 背景：当时邵典老师上热搜，我迷之自信就发邮件了。 当时大三、基本上都是跟着自己本科院校的项目、没有太多亮点（现在来说是有点井底之蛙 + 迷之自信的）； 之后就没有跟自己的本科院校做项目了：就去开源社区找项目、查国外工业软件的开发文档、去具体的企业实习。 现在，现在从业了，又想起来这个问题，觉得自己还是有没弄明白的地方，对于科研和工程。（我本科的科研实验室用的都还是比较旧的设备、技术、代码...，我觉得科研应该不是这样的。） 所以我现在的诉求是探讨科研和工程，考研和读研的区别也很大，如果以后自己有读研的打算，我也想了解一下科研是什么，如果我不适合做研究，我就立刻止损，不在自己不擅长的领域死磕。"},"attached_info":"CkAIhtTp3faKoNEcEAMaCTExMDAzMTE1NCC8upa2BjAAOOoBQAZyCTY2NDg5MTI3NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"140 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e599af0410c714c6000dd954e24ed641_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1724739782.219630","card_id":"Q_665326696","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":665326696,"title":"为什么中国的狐狸精喜欢偷吃鸡，日本的狐狸精喜欢偷吃油豆腐?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665326696","type":"question","created":1724645956,"answer_count":32,"follower_count":63,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[229,5823,12230,44081,99106],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"这里面有什么原因吗？是不是日本狐狸吃素?给玉藻前一份烧鸡和油豆腐，她会先吃什么?"},"attached_info":"Cj8IhtTp3faKoNEcEAMaCTExMDEyNzk3NSDEhLC2BjAAOD9AB3IJNjY1MzI2Njk2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"127 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-dc11773a4c9abc3163abf081260eb8a9_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1724739782.220177","card_id":"Q_665161741","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":665161741,"title":"一个二维码可以存2KB信息，使用很多个二维码是否能实现传文件？","url":"https://api.zhihu.c